txt.en: The dread morroval Iarvael has been hunting down the Council of the North. You must gather your allies and destroy her before she discovers their refuge. Her lair lies somewhere to the north of Bail Dílas in Angmar.

'There is a deadly creature laired just beyond the outskirts of Carn Dûm - a morroval named Iarvael who has learned of the existence of the Council of the North, and has begun to hunt down their forces one by one as they risk their lives to delay the growth of Angmar's power. She must be stopped, [placeholder]!\n\n'Gather your most stalwart allies and hunt her down before she should discover the hidden refuge of the Council.'
You must hunt down and defeat Iarvael, who is laired in the hills north of Bail Dílas.
'I have received a missive from the Wardens telling me of your heroic efforts in support of their cause, I thank you for taking such risks on their behalf and ours.'
Tell Handarod in Esteldín of your victory in Angmar.
